\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 has more rooms, bigger floor area and cheaper price than 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{2}$
\end_inset

) therefore we exclude 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{2}$
\end_inset

